# Legacy v0.1 prompts directory — canonical location is src/lre/data/prompts/
# (importlib.resources picks them up after wheel install). The top-level
# `data/prompts/` dir is honoured for backward-compat in the loader but
# never repopulated by the harness; ignore it so it cannot be recreated
# accidentally and cause divergent suite listings.
/data/
/data/prompts/
